Inspire Cooldown TimerInspireDescID: Displays a timer for the inspire cooldown.
Inspire Cooldown TimerTimerXDescID:
Change the horisontal position of the timer. 
 The change will be visible next time the timer shows up on the screen.
Inspire Cooldown TimerTimerYDescID:
Change the vertical position of the timer. 
 The change will be visible next time the timer shows up on the screen.
